Really? What would l need to do?

270
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:46,717
Officially, you provide
the baby with spiritual guidance.

271
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:50,634
Unofficially, you stand with me
so l have somebody to roll my eyes at.

272
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:53,109
l don't know...spiritual guidance?

273
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:56,033
There's cake
from some bakery in Queens.

274
00:16:56,200 --> 00:17:01,718
- The sugary kind with the thick icing?
- Maybe even a buttercream cross.

275
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:05,839
Oh, now you're talking.
Spirituality and cake.

276
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:11,789
That night, Charlotte dragged me
to the fountain of belief.

277
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:15,919
lt was mostly women. Apparently,
women are the main market for hope.

278
00:17:16,080 --> 00:17:18,435
Would you like an affirmation?

