00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:09,319
- Did you want to be the godmother?
- No!

294
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:12,916
lt wouldn't kill you to acknowledge
that some things are sacred.

295
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:14,957
- l do...
- We're not talking.

296
00:18:15,120 --> 00:18:17,839
- We're not?
- No.

297
00:18:27,760 --> 00:18:29,910
Are we talking yet?

298
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:35,033
Let me know when we're talking.

299
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:43,392
l believe this is going to be
a very long evening.

300
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:50,669
l believe we are
the only normal people here.

301
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:57,829
l believe in the good in Charlotte,
who dragged me here against my will

302
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:01,595
when l wanted to stay home
and just be negative.

303
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:11,913
What does the gown look like?

304
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,272
Table for two.

305
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:20,517
You're trying to make me feel bad,
but that turns me on.

306
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,716
Right this way.

307
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:40,198
Thank you.

308
00:19:44,840 --> 00:19:48,150
- Are we OK?
- We're fine.

309
00:19:48,320 --> 00:19:52,598
l almost forgot. You're going to
Miranda's baptism with me Sunday.

310
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:55,274
lt'll be all day, it'll be boring,
it'll be mandatory.

311
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:57,829
- What time?
- 2:00.

312
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:04,075
- Are you going to do the thing again?
- No. Are you?

313
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,548
Samantha, l love you.

314
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:15,873
Although he appeared
to have reformed,

315
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:18,600
Samantha wasn't ready
to forgive his sin.

316
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:23,390
Love will come to you only
when you truly believe you deserve it.

317
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:26,996
Meanwhile, an hour
and 20 affirmations later...

318
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:33,190
Love will raise you up. Fear will pull
you under. Only love is real.

319
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:35,191
Yes, stand up.

320
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:41,037
l wanted to thank you. The affirmations
have really worked for me.

321
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:45,591
l prayed for love, l believed in love,
and last week l fell in love.

322
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:50,311
He's perfect and kind and giving,
and l now know

323
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:52,516
that l deserve that. Thank you.

324
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:56,878
Thank yourself. You did it.
lsn't that inspiring? Yeah.

325
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:06,276
Anyone else?

326
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:11,152
- Did you want to say something?
- Oh, no...

327
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:14,278
Yes. Hi. l was wondering...

328
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:23,351
Hi... l'm wondering how long
that woman was doing her affirmations.

329
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:25,829
l've been doing mine every day.

330
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:29,754
l want to believe,
but nothing is happening.

331
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:36,036
l just don't think it's working.
l don't think it will work for me.

332
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:40,033
l hear fear. l hear doubt.

333
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:44,152
You have to believe love
to receive love.

334
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:48,359
Keep repeating your affirmations.
Your heart will catch up with your head.

335
00:21:50,120 --> 00:21:52,190
That's the thing, though.

336
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:54,316
l did find love.

337
00:21:55,000 --> 00:22:00,199
l believed there was someone out
there for me and l met him finally.

338
00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:04,399
We had a beautiful wedding,
and then everything just fell apart.

339
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:09,714
l'm worried. l'm afraid
that he took away my ability to believe.

340
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:13,839
l hate him for that
because l always believed before.

341
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:17,037
And now l just feel...lost.

342
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:24,352
And l am, l'm trying to put myself
out there but...l feel hopeless.

343
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:29,999
Perhaps you're not
really putting yourself out there.

344
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:32,071
Oh...

345
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:36,476
No, she's out there.

346
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,631
l mean emotionally and physically.

347
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:42,952
Maybe you're not looking for love
in a real way.

348
00:22:43,120 --> 00:22:46,715
Maybe you're not really trying.
Maybe you're not really out there.

349
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:49,838
Believe me. She's out there.

350
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:05,718
Sunday afternoon, we gathered for a
baptism in the little church that would.

351
