00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:33,789
Don't you think
l'm getting a little cynical?

372
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:36,474
Not compared to me.

373
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,710
You're my best friend.

374
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:45,272
Charlotte's dying for the job,
and l think she'd be better at it.

375
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:49,752
l don't know if l believe in any of this,
but l believe in you.

376
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:53,037
